    "content": {
      "rendered": "<div id=\"attachment_14751\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14751\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-14751 \" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Via Zoo Atlanta: Polar Bear Cubs (Endangered)\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/The-Power-of-Kawaii.jpg?w=467&amp;ssl=1 467w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-14751\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Via Zoo Atlanta: Polar Bear Cubs (Endangered)</p></div>\n<p>Looking at cute images, particularly those of baby animals, has been proven to increase\u00a0our brain&#8217;s concentration levels for a short time afterwards. The <a href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/japanrealtime/2012/09/29/study-shows-power-of-cute-improves-concentration/\">Power of<em> Kawaii</em></a> (a Japanese word meaning \u201ccute\u201d) can help nonprofit social media managers be more productive and also help counterbalance the flood of negative images that we are exposed to as a by-product of emerging ourselves into the 24/7 news cycle.\u00a0Thus, to boost your productivity and your spirits, have a quick scan of the images below and follow on Pinterest the five nonprofits listed to gain steady access to images that invoke the power of kawaii:</p>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/thedswt/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14740\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"baby elephant\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-elephant.jpg?resize=452%2C678\" width=\"452\" height=\"678\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-elephant.jpg?w=452&amp;ssl=1 452w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-elephant.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" /></a><strong>Via <a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/thedswt/\">David Sheldrick Wildlife Trust</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/apeactionafrica/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14741\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"baby gorilla 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-gorilla-2.jpg?resize=452%2C657\" width=\"452\" height=\"657\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-gorilla-2.jpg?w=452&amp;ssl=1 452w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-gorilla-2.jpg?resize=206%2C300&amp;ssl=1 206w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" /></a><strong>Via <a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/apeactionafrica/\">Ape Action Africa</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/zooatlanta/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14742\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"NRDC Giraffe\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NRDC-Giraffe.jpg?resize=452%2C585\" width=\"452\" height=\"585\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NRDC-Giraffe.jpg?w=452&amp;ssl=1 452w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NRDC-Giraffe.jpg?resize=231%2C300&amp;ssl=1 231w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" /></a><strong>Via <a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/zooatlanta/\">Zoo Atlanta</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/nrdcbiogems/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14743\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"NRDC Seals\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NRDC-Seals.jpg?resize=452%2C512\" width=\"452\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NRDC-Seals.jpg?w=452&amp;ssl=1 452w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/NRDC-Seals.jpg?resize=264%2C300&amp;ssl=1 264w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" /></a><strong>Via <a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/nrdcbiogems/\">NRDC BioGems</a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/wwfuk/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14746\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"baby jaguar wwf\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-jaguar-wwf.jpg?resize=452%2C339\" width=\"452\" height=\"339\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-jaguar-wwf.jpg?w=452&amp;ssl=1 452w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/baby-jaguar-wwf.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 452px) 100vw, 452px\" /></a><strong>Via <a href=\"http://www.pinterest.com/wwfuk/\">World Wildlife Fund</a></strong></p>\n",
